HEADWORD: Dermoid
<hw>Der"moid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Derm</ets> +
<ets>-oid</ets>: cf. F. <ets>dermo⟦ium⟧de</ets>.]</ety> <def>Same as
